// tgdev device: a shape built from STRUCTURED components (`pos`/`vel` are each an `(x, y)` pair) and a
// system that integrates position by velocity, addressing the group fields as `pos.x` / `vel.y`. Support
// file, not a standalone test.
// RUN: true
Mover :: arche { pos, vel }

integrate :: map (pos, vel) {
  pos.x = pos.x + vel.x;
  pos.y = pos.y + vel.y;
}
